<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV22">
<l>kompār taḻaikai ciṟunā ṇeṟivilam vēṭṭaikoṇṭāṭ</l>
<l>ṭampār kaḷiṟu viṉavuva taiyarpuḷ ḷūruṅkaḷvar</l>
<l>tampā rakatteṉṟu māṭā taṉatammiṟ kūṭātaṉa</l>
<l>vampār viṉāccolla vōvemmai vaittativ vāṉpuṉattē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord’s pretending , a branch full of foliage in hand, a hunt with a bow throwing [arrows]</l>
<l>with little string,  [and] asking about an elephant bull full of arrows,</l>
<l>[his] keeping us in this pure field, [is it] in order to ask useless questions</l> 
<l>that are never asked in the world of the robber who rides the bird, that are not met with in him?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
